Midnight Ravers
Life is in motion and Midnight Ravers are designed for it. Bright, unique, beautiful and durable enough to handle late nights of grooving to the music. These are designed to take the hardest of bass lines while letting you feel every note. The sound is definitely soul-satisfying.

name: Water Dancing Speakers
description:
Sometimes just listening to music isn't enough, so how about being able to see it in action too? These water-filled speakers not only sound great, they'll also dance along to the rhythm of your tunes as the fountains light up with coloured LEDs.

Features:

    Amazing water show speakers
    Water dances to the music
    Illuminated by 4 LEDs
    Connect to any music source with a 3.5mm jack
    No batteries required (powered by USB or mains power)
    Black rubberised base
    Measures approx. - 22cm x 6cm x 6cm (each)

name: Infinity Bluetooth Wireless Headphones with Music Controls and Call Mic
description: Our Infinity range of Bluetooth Headphones combine sound quality, style, practicality and affordability in to one great product. Listen to your music or audio from any Bluetooth device without the restrictions that come with wires. Move freely around your bedroom or office while your device sits charging in its dock. Or, even pop your phone into your pocket or bag and carry on listening to your music without feeding leads through your clothing. No tangles, no mess. Just stay within 10 meters of your device for great sound!

name: Samsung Galaxy Premium Earphones
description:
OFFICIAL ACCESSORY

Samsung 3.5mm Hands-free Stereo Headset is for you to use to carry hands-free calls via your cell/mobile phone or just enjoy listening to music on your phone. It is suitable for most cell phones, PDAs, portable games and music players with any standard 3.5 mm hands-free headset / headphone jack available. Includes a call answer button and volume button. Also comes with extra Ear Buds.
Compatible for use with other devices having a 3.5mm jack
